text: Kacha () is the name of several rural localities in Russia: *Kacha, Krasnoyarsk Krai, a settlement in Zeledeyevsky Selsoviet of Yemelyanovsky District in Krasnoyarsk Krai *Kacha, Sevastopol, a settlement in Nakhimovsky District of the federal city of SevastopolThe federal city of Sevastopol is a federal subject of Russia established on the territory of the Crimean Peninsula, which is a territory disputed between Russia and Ukraine. ==Notes==
title: Kacha, Russia
